'''Vulg., offensive, slang'''

An offensive name for the female genital organ in [[Slovak]]. Usualy used as an [[insult]], it is not normaly used in normal conversation — the word has a very negative conotation. 

== Usage ==

Smrdí ako '''piča'''. <br>Smells like a [[cunt]] (eg. a bad smell).<br><br>
Condoleezza je '''piča'''!<br>Condoleezza is a bitch.

== Grammar ==

'''piča''' ''f'' is declined using the [[ulica]] ([[street]]) [[paradigm]].

